Count 2 - Child Enticement - sexual contact - No contest plea.   Convicted.   State moves to dismiss and read in count 1, use a computer to facilitate a child sex crime.  Motion granted.   Sentence is withheld.  Defendant is placed on probation to DOC for thirty (30) months.   Conditions of probation are:
1) Assessment/treatment/counseling as deemed appropriate by the Department's assessment process;
2) Register and comply with sex offender registry;
3) No use or possession of a smartphone;
4) No use or possession of internet capable/enabled devices without agent's approval;
5) No contact with minors unless approved by agent;
6) Provide DNA sample and pay surcharge;
7) Six (6) months Manitowoc County Jail, stayed, to be imposed at agent's discretion; 
8) Pay costs of action;
9) Pay supervision fees in an amount to be determined by DOC.  
Minutes.
